### Seed ClubElo snapshot
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/elo/seed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_str": "2024-08-01",
  "season": "2024"
}

###

### Recalculate ELO ratings (SFA internal IDs: La Liga=1, PL=3, Bundesliga=6, Serie A=7, Ligue 1=9)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/elo/recalculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "season": "2024",
  "competition_ids": [1, 3, 6, 7, 9],
  "k_factors": {
    "1": 30,
    "3": 30,
    "6": 30,
    "7": 30,
    "9": 30
  },
  "default_k": 30.0
}

###

### Recalculate ELO with higher K for Champions League (SFA internal ID: Champions League=10)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/elo/recalculate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "season": "2024",
  "competition_ids": [1, 3, 10],
  "k_factors": {
    "1": 30,
    "3": 30,
    "10": 35
  },
  "default_k": 30.0
}

###

### Error case: invalid date
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/admin/elo/seed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_str": "not-a-date",
  "season": "2024"
}
